description:
Sponsored by UK Export Finance

Entrepreneur David Olusegun shares his inspiring journey behind cofounding SYPS, a healthy, bold-flavored drink created as an alternative to sugary energy drinks. He highlights the challenges Black-owned businesses face when securing finance and expanding internationally, and the crucial role UK Export Finance can play in helping these businesses fulfil their export ambitions. 

From local to global - UK Export Finance: https://www.ukexportfinance.gov.uk/from-local-to-global/
